                            <comment id="17844277" author="epugh" created="Tue, 7 May 2024 12:57:11 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;I think this commit broke errorprone?&#160;&#160; I am seeing:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&#160;&lt;br/&gt;
 Task :solr:core:compileTestJava FAILED &lt;br/&gt;
&#160;&lt;br/&gt;
/home/runner/work/solr/solr/solr/core/src/test/org/apache/solr/util/TimeZoneUtilsTest.java:65: warning: &lt;span class=&quot;error&quot;&gt;&amp;#91;OperatorPrecedence&amp;#93;&lt;/span&gt; Use grouping parenthesis to make the operator precedence explicit &lt;br/&gt;
&#160;&lt;br/&gt;
