&#160;&lt;br/&gt;
 Did you mean &apos;if ((expected.useDaylightTime() &amp;amp;&amp;amp; expected.getDSTSavings() == 0)&apos;? &lt;br/&gt;
&#160;&lt;br/&gt;
/home/runner/work/solr/solr/solr/core/src/test/org/apache/solr/util/TimeZoneUtilsTest.java:66: warning: &lt;span class=&quot;error&quot;&gt;&amp;#91;OperatorPrecedence&amp;#93;&lt;/span&gt; Use grouping parenthesis to make the operator precedence explicit &lt;br/&gt;
&#160;&lt;/p&gt;
