&#160;&lt;br/&gt;
 ^ &lt;br/&gt;
&#160;&lt;br/&gt;
 (see &lt;a href=&quot;https://errorprone.info/bugpattern/OperatorPrecedence)&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://errorprone.info/bugpattern/OperatorPrecedence)&lt;/a&gt; &lt;br/&gt;
